# cut the rope type game For Android
## cut the rope type game For Android using BOX2D and view canvas draw


 [GooglePlay link](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kd.grabandcut.menu)

Cut the rope , grab the star and go next level- - Game is in beta phase Gameplay: Cut the rope collect all star Go in right door EATURES • Cute and friendly graphics and sounds • Simple single-tap gameplay • Munch through two bug filled worlds • Day and Night cycles bring new bugs to eat and new dangers to avoid • See how many days you can feed Froad for • Universal App – Optimized for both your handheld and tablet device • Over 60 Achievements to unlock • And 6 Leaderboards to climb Developed by: Kishor datta gupta.
